### 测试 Saga 编排器

### 执行成功的 Saga 流程
POST http://localhost:8080/api/saga/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "productId": "product456",
  "quantity": 2,
  "amount": 99.99
}

### 执行会失败的 Saga 流程（金额过大）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/saga/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "productId": "product456",
  "quantity": 2,
  "amount": 1500.00
}

### 查询 Saga 状态
GET http://localhost:8080/api/saga/SAGA_123456

